START: Hostel-Register
    Get the user's hostel which in duty
    IF new record is written in the database
        read the enrollment number, destination and time of the record
        Fetch the student's name and hostel from students database
        Convert time to readable format
        IF record's hostel matches with the Hostel on duty
            Print the enrollment number, name, destination, and time.
    Else Continue the loop
